<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>د ل ك<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[١٨٣٥ - د ل ك]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>دلَكَ٢ يَدلُك، دُلُوكًا، فهو دالِك<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• دلَكتِ الشَّمسُ:</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>١ - زالَتْ عن كبد السَّماء، اصفَرَّت ومالت للغروب <span class="c1">" <span class="c3">{أَقِمِ الصَّلاَةَ لِدُلُوكِ الشَّمْسِ}</span> "</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>٢ - غابت؛ لأنّ الناظرَ إليها يدلِك عينَه.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>